OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud clearing England and
OL,6,FWales to leave another dry and sunny
OL,7,Fday. Sunny in Northern Ireland, but
OL,8,Fcloudier across much of Scotland.
OL,9,FFeeling hot in the sunshine, but
OL,10,Ffresher in the east with a breeze.
OL,11,FWindy along southern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,14,Fsunshine for many. Patchy low cloud
OL,15,Fwill form in eastern and central
OL,16,Fareas, otherwise fine and dry with
OL,17,Flong clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
