OL,5,CMonday:FLow cloud clearing through the
OL,6,Fmorning with many areas dry and sunny.
OL,7,FBrisk easterly winds with gales along
OL,8,Fsome southern and western coasts. Hot
OL,9,Fagain in southwest England and Wales.
